{"tid":2233387,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【TikTok】報告指TikTok超越Instagram 成美國青年第二喜愛社交App","createTime":"2020-10-07T05:47:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T06:27:40.000Z","uid":51665,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"54ca60455238fe7256ceb54ebbaceb954d8c4a8b","tid":2233387,"uid":51665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T05:47:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2770000/2770751/1007008_600.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2770000%2F2770751%2F1007008_600.png&h=cac3605e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國下令封禁中國短片分享平台抖音海外版TikTok之際，最新一份報告顯示，TikTok已超越Instagram，成為美國青少年中第二受歡迎的社交媒體應用，僅次於Snapchat。<br />\n<br />\nCNBC報道，投行Piper Sandler周二（6日）發布報告顯示，34%的青少年將Snapchat列為最喜歡社交應用，其次是TikTok（29%），Instagram排第三（25%）。<br />\n<br />\n使用量情況不同<br />\n<br />\n但報告指出，使用情況則是另一番光景。使用量方面，Instagram仍是用戶參與度最高的App，達到84%，其次是Snapchat（80%）和TikTok（69%）。<br />\n<br />\n報告表示，TikTok在美國年輕用戶市場份額持續增加。這類用戶是廣告主的主要針對人群，而廣告收入則是社交媒體應用的主要收入來源。<br />\n<br />\n為規避TikTok威脅，Facebook今年8月在旗下Instagram推出短片服務Reels，類似TikTok容許用家錄製短影片，料瓜分TikTok海外市場。<br />\n<br />\n根本美豬中哂支共病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />牙祖稱帝同習帝稱兄道弟係大概率事項<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b42615a8c4c43add4b5a96d233ce2794d2539c05","tid":2233387,"uid":328199,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T05:50:45.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"54ae7b6b3b36414cc89d0786cdc8009fb5cdfaa8","tid":2233387,"uid":271199,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T05:59:54.000Z","msg":"被支共洗曬腦，太多美豬"},{"pid":"d868a0cc96f1467d0eaaecb1fa7cc04ea24581a1","tid":2233387,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T06:27:40.000Z","msg":"事實抖音拍十幾秒片扮明星係好吸引班MK玩，而班MK又唔會理政治。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}